      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add<strong> half </strong>of<strong> </strong>the<strong> chopped tomatoes </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to a baking tray with a little drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 7-8 min or until the tomatoes have started to blister</p>",
