    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped wholemeal pitta</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> half</strong> your <strong>ground sumac </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and<strong> </strong>a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>to the blistered tomatoes</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 4-5 min or until the pitta has begun to crisp up – this is your <strong>crispy sumac pitta</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
