            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>pomegranate molasses</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>honey & molasses dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
