        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Assemble the salad with the<strong> crispy sumac pitta</strong> and <strong>roasted tomatoes </strong>first, then layer on the <strong>sliced</strong> and <strong>quartered</strong> <strong>radishes</strong>,<strong> remaining chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>cucumber</strong> <strong>batons</strong> and <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> mint</strong></p><p>Crumble over your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> and sprinkle over the <strong>reserved ground sumac</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>honey & molasses dressing </strong>all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
